OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FJohn Swinney has stepped up his calls
OL,7,Ffor Holyrood to be given control over
OL,8,Fenergy, insisting it is the only way
OL,9,Fto end the current "Westminster rip-
OL,10,Foff".
OL,12,FThe Scottish First Minister said
OL,13,Fhanding over energy powers would allow
OL,14,Fhis Government to end the "hated"
OL,15,Fwindfall tax on oil and gas ` formally
OL,16,Fknown as the energy profits levy.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@DO]vD@[OUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FHe also said it would allow for
OL,7,F"sensible licensing decisions" to be
OL,8,Ftaken on new energy projects, and
OL,9,Fcould cut bills for people across
OL,10,FScotland.
OL,12,FHe was speaking ahead of campaigning
OL,13,Fin Aberdeen ` where much of the UK's
OL,14,Foil and gas industry is based ` in the
OL,15,Frun-up to a Commons by-election.
OL,17,FThe vote in Aberdeen South is taking
OL,18,Fplace after former SNP Westminster
OL,19,Fleader Stephen Flynn won a seat at
OL,20,FHolyrood earlier this month.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FEnergy is already a key issue ahead of
OL,7,Fthe June 18 by-election, with
OL,8,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,9,Furging voters in the constituency to
OL,10,Fmake it a referendum on the future of
OL,11,FScotland's oil and gas sector.
OL,13,FMr Swinney's visit on Saturday comes
OL,14,Fafter the regulator Ofgem announced
OL,15,Fthe energy price cap is to rise in
OL,16,FJuly, and after MSPs backed a call for
OL,17,Fpower over the sector to be
OL,18,Ftransferred to Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FThe First Minister said:
OL,7,F"Westminster's energy rip-off of our
OL,8,Fcountry was in full view this week `
OL,9,FWestminster controls Scotland's
OL,10,Fenergy, the UK Treasury rakes in
OL,11,Fbillions from our seabed, and Scots
OL,12,Fare left paying the price with higher
OL,13,Fenergy bills.
OL,15,F"#400 billion has been syphoned off
OL,16,Ffrom our North Sea and the only way to
OL,17,Fbreak that rigged energy equation is
OL,18,Fby putting Scotland's energy into
OL,19,FScotland's hands.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,F"Time and time again Westminster
OL,7,Fparties come to the north east not to
OL,8,Ftalk about how they can support the
OL,9,Findustry, but how they can milk every
OL,10,Flast penny from Scotland while sending
OL,11,Fback nothing in return.
OL,13,F"Instead of Scotland's energy working
OL,14,Ffor Westminster, it's time that our
OL,15,Fenergy worked for our people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,F"By putting Scotland's energy in
OL,7,FScotland's hands we can end the hated
OL,8,Ftax on our energy, we can take
OL,9,Fsensible licensing decisions based on
OL,10,FScotland's needs, but most importantly
OL,11,Fwe can lower bills for people living
OL,12,Fin our energy rich land."
OL,14,FHe vowed the SNP will "never stand by
OL,15,Fas Westminster casts workers in
OL,16,FAberdeen on the scrapheap", with Mr
OL,17,FSwinney saying the SNP could "protect
OL,18,Fthe world-class oil and gas sector we
OL,19,Fhave today and build another world-
OL,20,Fclass renewables industry right by its
OL,21,Fside".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]vD@WOUxD@ZO]yD@^OU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FHitting out at his political rivals,
OL,7,Fthe First Minister added: "We cannot
OL,8,Fallow Nigel Farage or the Tories to
OL,9,Fget their hands on our energy wealth
OL,10,Fhere in Aberdeen South.
OL,12,F"Only the SNP can beat them both and
OL,13,Fensure our natural resources are used
OL,14,Fto the benefit of the people of
OL,15,FScotland."
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FWhile the Scottish Government has
OL,7,Fcalled for the windfall tax to be
OL,8,Fended, Simon Francis, co-ordinator of
OL,9,Fthe End Fuel Poverty Coalition, said
OL,10,Fvoters from all parties support the
OL,11,Flevy.
OL,13,FMr Francis said: "Politicians may
OL,14,Fparrot the oil and gas lobbyists' line
OL,15,Fthat the windfall tax is hated, but
OL,16,Fthe public disagrees.
OL,18,F"Polling in the run-up to the Scottish
OL,19,Felections found voters across all
OL,20,Fparties supported the energy profits
OL,21,Flevy.
OL,26,@uD@ROUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,F"What's more, following revelations
OL,7,Fthat the oil and gas industry made #3
OL,8,Fbillion in profits on UK operations in
OL,9,Fthe first three months of 2026, three-
OL,10,Fquarters of the population felt it is
OL,11,Fmorally wrong for oil and gas
OL,12,Fcompanies to profit from the energy
OL,13,Fcrisis caused by the Iran war."
OL,15,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,16,FFindlay said: "John Swinney is fooling
OL,17,Fno-one with his desperate and
OL,18,Fdishonest nonsense. This is classic
OL,19,FSNP grievance politics.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@_O]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,F"Voters know that the SNP, just like
OL,7,FLabour, oppose new drilling in the
OL,8,FNorth Sea.
OL,10,F"The SNP demanded a windfall tax,
OL,11,FLabour have extended it, while we
OL,12,Fwould scrap it.
OL,14,F"Only the Scottish Conservatives can
OL,15,Fbeat the SNP in Aberdeen South."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
