PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said:
OL,8,F"Our number one priority is lowering
OL,9,Fbills, which remain high because
OL,10,Fwholesale costs, the single largest
OL,11,Fcomponent of the price cap, are higher
OL,12,Fthan their historic levels.
OL,14,F"Oil and gas production will be with
OL,15,Fus for decades to come, and we will
OL,16,Fmanage existing fields for the
OL,17,Fentirety of their lifespan ` while
OL,18,Factively scaling up clean energy
OL,19,Findustries in the North Sea.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780102991
OL,3,CSwinney steps up calls to end
OL,4,C'Westminster rip-off' over energy
OL,6,F"The way to get bills down for good is
OL,7,Fwith this Government's drive for clean
OL,8,Fhomegrown power we control, bringing
OL,9,Finvestment and up to 40,000 new jobs
OL,10,Fin Scotland by 2030."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]
